timelineItems.text: 83' Another great break form the 'Caps but Rivero can't find Mattocks. Still 1-0 #VWFC #LAvVAN

timelineItems.name: Adam Serrano
timelineItems.text: 83' Ishizaki's corner hits Ousted in the midsection and then sparks a Whitecaps counter that sputters out. #LAvVAN

timelineItems.name: Andrew âÙ
timelineItems.text: I thought we were paying Rivero to score... Why isn't he shooting? #VWFC

timelineItems.name: Tyler Green
timelineItems.text: Rivero set up a beautiful pass and Morales couldn't finish and then gave a shocking pass to Mattocks on a carbon copy play #LAvVAN

timelineItems.name: LA Galaxy
timelineItems.text: Just over five minutes left here. Can the #LAGalaxy grab a late equalizer? http://t.co/3uZxGcwUeL #LAvVAN http://t.co/7LRpqNNByt

timelineItems.name: Andrew Schmidt
timelineItems.text: This is some seriously uninspired movement from the Galaxy. Bad switches and desperate crosses. Out of ideas. #LAvVAN

timelineItems.name: Matt Pollard
timelineItems.text: 86' Keane and Gordon cancel each other out on a header in the box. Cleared. Smh. #LAGalaxy #LAvVAN

timelineItems.name: Vancouver Whitecaps
timelineItems.text: 87' Mattocks races clear but has his pocket picked by Leonardo. #VWFC #LAvVAN

timelineItems.name: Rob Freeman
timelineItems.text: Caps should be 3 up, done and dusted. #VWFC

timelineItems.name: Corner Of The Galaxy
timelineItems.text: Here’s a hint for the @WhitecapsFC for their fast break: Go around Leonardo. #LAGalaxy #MLS #LAvVAN

timelineItems.name: Women United FC
timelineItems.text: Definitely get the sense there was a meltdown, that they were taken apart piece by piece. They're frustrated and it shows. #LAGalaxy

timelineItems.name: Joe Tansey
timelineItems.text: Watching 1 Cascadia team (#rctid) finish off a game & the other (#vwfc) fail to put the Galaxy to rest. That's a bit of a role reversal.

timelineItems.name: Jamie Vodden
timelineItems.text: It's not too late, Stevie. Absolutely shocking. #LAGalaxy @InfectiousChris http://t.co/5zicC0gRw5

timelineItems.name: Collin Marshall
timelineItems.text: The blown chances by the Whitecaps are growing by the minute. An ongoing storyline for a few years. #whitecapsfc

timelineItems.name: AFTN
timelineItems.text: Kah: You have cramp Robbie. Let me help. Keane: No I don't. I'm fine. Kah: You do. You just lie there while I bend your legs! #LAvVAN

timelineItems.name: LA Galaxy WUFC
timelineItems.text: 4 minutes stoppage. #LAvVAN

timelineItems.name: LA Galaxy WUFC
timelineItems.text: There is still time if we just make the most of it. #LAvVAN

timelineItems.name: Challengers Podcast
timelineItems.text: Robbie Keane probably could never do a bicycle kick, but it was proven right there. But Kah stretching him out after was hilarious. #LAvVAN

timelineItems.name: Corner Of The Galaxy
timelineItems.text: #LAGalaxy still without a shot on goal. #LAvVAN

timelineItems.name: Chris Wilhelm
timelineItems.text: How many times has an #LAGalaxy player kicked the ball right at someone for Vancouver this evening? Just bad. #LAvVAN
